{"tid":887853,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇見過咁靚仔嘅監躉","createTime":"2018-11-03T08:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T02:47:00.000Z","uid":90316,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a0d44273c096e20f343e463591036fb620b31c","tid":887853,"uid":90316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T08:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RgFDQZj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRgFDQZj.gif&h=c0c70436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我的名字是何志武，坐牢的編號是二二三。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LWjX6yu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLWjX6yu.png&h=ead34b3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8FgohFc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8FgohFc.png&h=03fed61a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每天你都會和很多人擦肩而過，那個人可能變成你的朋友，或者是知己。"},{"pid":"41f728a769a953d24958b93c645fc0dcadad167c","tid":887853,"uid":90316,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T08:58:14.000Z","msg":"一般人的初戀是在十幾歲，而我呢，可能比較晚熟吧，或者是要求比較高吧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v08xVsz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv08xVsz.png&h=2b87de11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n它就好象是一家店，我不知能停留多久，當然，越久越好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/63W317B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F63W317B.png&h=9e362d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我不該隨便打開別人的店，說來就來，就不來就不來。因為每一家店<br />\n，都是有感情的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJBGONF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJBGONF.png&h=41a3cfdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可是，這一分鐘，我覺得好暖。"},{"pid":"898d23f031bb20fecc1879f285fd9b02b09a0a34","tid":887853,"uid":90316,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T09:05:48.000Z","msg":"我聽人講過，任何東西都會過期的。我不知她和JOHNNY的感情什麼時候過期，不過我想，應該很快吧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7SyJ2bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7SyJ2bf.png&h=d76ba118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一直以為她和JOHNNY的感情會很快過期，可是誰知道，最快過期的，竟然是我。"},{"pid":"7cce68900dfedddd6f4f85df937509cfe8c1901d","tid":887853,"uid":32114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我不該隨便打開別人的店，說來就來，就不來就不來。因為每一家店<br />\n，都是有感情的。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以每打開別人的店，即使不合適自己，我還是會禮貌地向店東打個招呼，參觀一下門面，還會借一下廁所，最後便優雅地揚長而去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79445a7b1dd721e182fda2230e59766a3de09881","tid":887853,"uid":32114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7cce68900dfedddd6f4f85df937509cfe8c1901d","tid":887853,"uid":32114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我不該隨便打開別人的店，說來就來，就不來就不來。因為每一家店<br />\n，都是有感情的。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以每打開別人的店，即使不合適自己，我還是會禮貌地向店東打個招呼，參觀一下門面，還會借一下廁所，最後便優雅地揚長而去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T09:29:37.000Z","msg":"有些店東從此和我成了朋友，有些卻討厭我至極⋯⋯但更多的是把我從記憶中抹掉。<br />\n<br />\n不過共同的是，我都在她們店內渡過了美好的時光，也留下了不能磨滅的記號。"},{"pid":"da018028a3792c250a13a1db3b3493620066f89b","tid":887853,"uid":119330,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T09:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20130726/large/1374808957_46cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20130726%2Flarge%2F1374808957_46cf.jpg&h=aa6f5490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牠的名字是劉馬車, 外號天水圍墮天地獸<br />\n每天你都會睇到好多新聞消息, 那個人可能是非禮犯, 或者是強姦犯"},{"pid":"7f8e3210d97401203f7710e6dae84a741d689894","tid":887853,"uid":154871,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T09:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/03/174145_e3214d0f0793f7c4745a38aa9da287b3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.